title: ImageMacro
tags: docs macro

The ImageMacro displays an image with an optional tooltip.

! Parameters

! Examples

{{{
<<tiddler [[Motovun Jack.jpg]]>>
}}}

Appears as:

<<tiddler [[Motovun Jack.jpg]]>>

{{{
<<image [[Motovun Jack.jpg]] text:"A kitten">>
}}}

Appears as:

<<image [[Motovun Jack.jpg]] text:"A kitten">>

(Hover over the image to see the tooltip).
